---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 93
By: Boethius
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Hold of Passion
---
Whosoever will remember his lusts shall understand that the end of pleasure
is sadness.  Which if it be able to cause happiness, there is no reason why
beasts should not be thought blessed, whose whole intention is bent to supply
their corporal wants.
